{"tid":1129784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★中港牌私家車衝入和合石墳場　撞毀多個墓碑","createTime":"2019-04-28T15:45:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-28T16:33:27.000Z","uid":19454,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"78bb3d267411442da3fabee85f4e24c6a329713f","tid":1129784,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T15:45:21.000Z","msg":"粉嶺和合石墳場發生車禍，今日(28日)下午5時許，一名姓翁(61歲)男子駕駛掛中港牌私家車，倒後時疑誤入前波令私家車急速衝前，失控掃毀8米長鐵欄及3條鐵柱後，再剷入一個私人墓園，撞毀多個墳墓。警方及消防接後到場調查，翁沒有受傷，警方將意外列作交通意外無人受傷及政府財物損毀。事後，有網民將意外照片上載到facebook群組，網民紛紛留言，有人擔心中港車司機的駕駛安全問題，另有網民則稱「今晚大把老友記搵佢」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190428/bkn-20190428194810733-0428_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190428%2Fbkn-20190428194810733-0428_00822_001.html&d=chjGuQxbuHnWuKCrZ0KyvsyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=f7f2beb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190428/bkn-20190428194810733-0428_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"5af26c87afeb0f0bac88274350d774a4b7203dcf","tid":1129784,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T15:45:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190428/photo/bkn-20190428194810733-0428_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190428205956\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190428%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190428194810733-0428_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190428205956&h=ad474076&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"35db102e0eb3b44049386845862234fe747e3af0","tid":1129784,"uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T15:46:58.000Z","msg":"支鬼Vs真鬼？"},{"pid":"78cbcb3e4ae226db6390afe18c03e4614f51cbe7","tid":1